- 'Available on multiple platforms' means the game is listed on more than one platform;
- 'Free-to-play' and 'multiplayer' are specific tags that a game must have.

sql:
SELECT MAX(game_count) AS max_total_games
FROM (
    SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT game_id) AS game_count
    FROM game_platforms
    GROUP BY platform_id
) AS platform_game_count;

SELECT game_id
FROM game_platforms
WHERE platform_id = 1;

